value.0: Please select your path? This selection is permanent.
Like pulling a loose thread, the monk tugs at the Weave with their Ki. This path unravels magical defenses and reshapes magic into unpredictable magical strikes.
Listen to the heartbeat of Ki that courses through all living things. This path is about striking powerful rhythmic stances that strengthen one's allies.
Like a stalwart gorgon, swords bounce off the monk's skin from the sheer flow of their Ki. This path isolates the body from the mind and makes it into an impenetrable fortress.
The monk becomes as the elements and turns into an unstoppable force of nature. This path channels Ki through elemental forces to deliver destructive strikes.
The monk finds clarity in ritual infliction of pain and suffering - to share their pain is to divide it. This path grows one's power for every injury sustained.
The monk becomes a conduit for the Ki of all living things which yearn to manifest through their will. This path creates Echoes - fractions of Ki that aid the monk on their journey and in combat.
In stillness, the monk uncovers inner strength and awakens an inner sight. This path is about using one's Ki to anticipate the future flow of the fight.
